text: Iquiracetima brachialis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1868. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Iquiracetima brachialis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1868
